### === VARIÁVEIS ===
### Defina @token com o valor do cookie AUTH_TOKEN após fazer login
### Para o perfil local: rode com -Dspring.profiles.active=local

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@adminToken = local-admin-token
@token = COLE_O_JWT_AQUI


### ====================================================================
###  HEALTH
### ====================================================================

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health


### ====================================================================
###  AUTH — Fluxo de registro e login local
### ====================================================================

### [1/4] Criar conta (envia email de verificação)
POST {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João Teste",
  "email": "joao@teste.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

### [2/4] Reenviar email de verificação (caso não tenha recebido)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/resend-verification
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@teste.com"
}

### [3/4] Verificar email (copie o token do link recebido no email)
### No perfil local o LogEmailService imprime o link no console do Spring
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/verify?token=TOKEN_DO_EMAIL

### [4/4] Login local
### Após o login o cookie AUTH_TOKEN é setado — copie-o para @token acima
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@teste.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

### ====================================================================
###  AUTH — Google OAuth
### ====================================================================

### Login com Google (token ID vindo do GSI)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/google
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "ID_TOKEN_DO_GOOGLE"
}


### ====================================================================
###  AUTH — Reset de senha
### ====================================================================

### [1/2] Solicitar reset de senha (envia email com token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/accounts/password/reset-request
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@teste.com"
}

### [2/2] Redefinir senha com o token do email
POST {{baseUrl}}/accounts/password/reset
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "novaSenha456",
  "token": "TOKEN_DO_EMAIL_DE_RESET"
}


### ====================================================================
###  ACCOUNTS
### ====================================================================

### Dados da conta autenticada
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/me
Cookie: AUTH_TOKEN={{token}}

### Histórico de transferências da conta 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/1/transfers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ====================================================================
###  CLIENTS
### ====================================================================

### Perfil do cliente autenticado
GET {{baseUrl}}/clients/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ====================================================================
###  ASSETS — Consultas públicas
### ====================================================================

### Listar todos os assets (com preço médio e supply)
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets

### Buscar asset por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets/1

### Histórico de preços de um asset (todas as listings)
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets/6/price-history

### Listar bundles (paginado)
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets/bundles?page=0&size=10

### Itens de um bundle
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets/bundles/1/items?page=0&size=20


### ====================================================================
###  ASSET UNITS — Units por dono
### ====================================================================

### Listar units da conta 1 (ownerId = accountId)
GET {{baseUrl}}/asset-units?ownerId=1&page=0&pageSize=10


### ====================================================================
###  ASSETS — Claim gratuito
### ====================================================================

### Verificar quando o próximo claim estará disponível
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets/claim
Cookie: AUTH_TOKEN={{token}}

### Resgatar um asset gratuito (assetId = ID do asset disponível)
POST {{baseUrl}}/assets/claim
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: AUTH_TOKEN={{token}}

{
  "assetId": 1
}


### ====================================================================
###  ASSET LISTINGS — Mercado
### ====================================================================

### Listar listings ativos (paginado)
GET {{baseUrl}}/asset-listings?page=0&pageSize=10
Cookie: AUTH_TOKEN={{token}}

### Meus listings ativos
GET {{baseUrl}}/asset-listings/me?page=0&pageSize=10
Cookie: AUTH_TOKEN={{token}}

### Buscar listing por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/asset-listings/1

### Histórico de preços de um listing
GET {{baseUrl}}/asset-listings/1/price-history

### Comprar um listing (ID do listing = 1)
POST {{baseUrl}}/asset-listings/1/purchase
Cookie: AUTH_TOKEN={{token}}


### ====================================================================
###  ASSET OFFERS — Criar e cancelar ofertas de venda
### ====================================================================

### Colocar asset à venda (assetUnityId = ID da unit que você possui)
POST {{baseUrl}}/asset-offers
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: AUTH_TOKEN={{token}}

{
  "assetUnityId": 1,
  "price": 200.00
}

### Cancelar oferta de venda (assetListingId = ID do listing criado acima)
POST {{baseUrl}}/asset-offers/cancel
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: AUTH_TOKEN={{token}}

{
  "assetListingId": 1
}


### ====================================================================
###  ADMIN — Operações administrativas
### ====================================================================

### Dar balance usando clientId (obtido via /accounts/me → campo "clientId")
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/accounts/deposit
Content-Type: application/json
X-Admin-Token: {{adminToken}}

{
  "clientId": 1,
  "amount": "1000.00"
}

### Dar balance usando o próprio JWT do usuário (sem precisar do clientId)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/accounts/deposit
Content-Type: application/json
X-Admin-Token: {{adminToken}}

{
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "amount": "1000.00"
}

### Gerar assets semanais
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/assets/generate
X-Admin-Token: {{adminToken}}

### Criar bundle de assets manualmente
POST {{baseUrl}}/assets/bundles
Content-Type: application/json
X-Admin-Token: {{adminToken}}

{
  "identifier": "weekly-2026-W26",
  "assets": [
    {
      "text": "Rare Lines #001",
      "totalSupply": 1
    },
    {
      "text": "Epic Lines #001",
      "totalSupply": 1
    }
  ]
}

### Criar unit de asset para uma conta (distribuição manual)
POST {{baseUrl}}/assets/1/units
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "ownerAccountId": 1,
  "token": "{{token}}"
}
